text: Compere or Compère is a French surname and may refer to: * Compere (host), a master of ceremonies == People == *Loyset Compère (c. 1445–1518), French composer of the Renaissance *Claude Antoine Compère (1774–1812), French general in the French Revolutionary Wars and the Napoleonic Wars *Louis Fursy Henri Compère (1768–1833), French general in the French Revolutionary Wars and the Napoleonic Wars *René Compère (1906–1969), Belgian jazz trumpeter *Adéodat Compère-Morel (1872–1941), French Socialist politician and agronomist *Léon Compère-Léandre (c. 1874–1936), Martiniquais shoemaker, survivor of the Mount Pelée eruption in 1902 == Film == * Les Compères, a 1983 French comedy film Category:French-language surnames
title: Compere
